{"id": "lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_NDY4Mg_0018", "text": "誰重要從未知 直到他不能留住 然後至知", "structure": {"line_index": 18, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 4, 0, 2, 3, 2, 4, 3, 3, 0, 0, 2, 0, 2, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "jiu3", "cung4", "mei6", "zi1", "zik6", "dou3", "taa1", "bat1", "nang4", "lau4", "zyu6", "jin4", "hau6", "zi3", "zi1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "重要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "從", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "直到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "留住", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "然後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "至知", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "相安無事", "artists": ["周柏豪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4682", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_NDY4Mg_0017", "next_line_id": "lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_NDY4Mg_0019", "paragraph_id": "para_07"}}
{"id": "lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_NDY4Mg_0019", "text": "我最想貪多一點 是無聊日子", "structure": {"line_index": 19, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 9, 3, 3, 3, 9, 2, 0, 0, 2, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "zeoi3", "soeng2", "taam1", "do1", "jat1", "dim2", "si6", "mou4", "liu4", "jat6", "zi2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "貪多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一點", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無聊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "日子", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "相安無事", "artists": ["周柏豪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4682", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_NDY4Mg_0018", "next_line_id": "lyr_5ZGo5p-P6LGq_NDY4Mg_0020", "paragraph_id": "para_08"}}
